Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCB3B17&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}在重逢的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCB3B17&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur7.5\fad(150,150)}You made me whole, you made me whole\N你完整了我的世界
